                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/ep3-doctrine/adding-more-columns.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>We're <em>close</em> to making the genus page dynamic - but it has a few fields that we don't
have yet - like sub family, number of known species, and fun fact.</p>
<p>Let's add these... and be as lazy as possible when we do it! In <code>Genus</code>, create the
properties first: <code>private $subFamily</code>, <code>private $speciesCount</code> and <code>private $funFact</code>:</p>
